		<descriptionSet>
			<description lang="eng" script="Latn">
				<text>On this lobby card for the Hindi movie &quot;Satyam Shivam Sundaram&quot;, released in 1978, the left section has a movie still of the two leading actors, Shashi Kapoor (Ranjeet) and Zeenat Aman (Rupa). Zeenat Aman is dancing in a shallow river wearing wet clothes as Shashi Kapoor looks towards her. Shashi Kapoor is also completely wet and is wearing a pair of shorts. In the background a tree on the banks of the river can be seen.
To the right of the image, under the emblem of Raj Kapoor Films, Zeenat Aman is shown again, wearing a revealing blouse and a tight, short dhoti wrapped in the style of a langot (cloth wrapped so it goes between the legs).</text>
				<author>
					<name vocab="local" type="personal" refid="uuid-d4f4f076-3fb9-5544-95bf-29ba8cb16992">Schoenhofer, Gerhard</name>
